      "side": 1,
      "message": "(I realize this is copy/pasted unchanged, but...)\n\nSeems like the branches could be up-to-date but the commits that the branches point to to be still missing, unless there\u0027s something in GitStore to account for that.\n\nOTOH, it seems like that could happen in production, and currently updateFromGitStore doesn\u0027t seem to handle that possibility.",
